summary: A preset for racemenu based on my Nord DB.
descriptionHtml:
This is a preset of my female Nord character Ylva. The only requirement is Racemenu, but she won't look the same unless you have the following installed:

[list]
[*][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] - I'm using the CBBE version but UNP should work just as well.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71561/?]SC Hairstyles[/url] - a small file containing a dozen or so hairstyles based on popular ones seen in Dragon Age[/size]
[*][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68355/]Hawke Blood Smear Warpaint[/url][/size]
[/list]
Installation: 
Extract file to C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

Uninstallation:
Delete jslot file from CharGen/Presets folder.
